{"tid":990431,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企用緊hisense電視","createTime":"2019-01-21T14:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T23:02:42.000Z","uid":177924,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"550b0ad083a4456949624a005c5bc38718c3ed32","tid":990431,"uid":177924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"好撚on9部垃圾電視勁多bugs<br />\n一唔小心轉台轉去奇妙電視/香港開電視呢啲濕鳩台<br />\n就成部機hang左<br />\n淨係可以睇果一台<br />\n較唔到聲音轉唔到台改唔到setting<br />\n轉去其它mode都係播緊同一個台既畫面<br />\n轉用上網睇片一樣睇一陣自己收皮去返電視mode<br />\n幾年前岩岩買就中過呢個bug<br />\n果陣要襯一開機就立即轉台/重新搜台去fix個bug<br />\n依家呢一招又用唔到<br />\n屋企人收工既唯一餘興節目都無埋<br />\n諗住7000幾蚊買電視就算係大陸野應該都唔會廢得去邊<br />\n點知中撚哂伏<br />\n屌你老母垃圾牌子<br />\n<br />\nBTW有無巴絲打有同樣問題<br />\n有無咩辦法可以自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901532f2f33f18d8bda0604deed7ef1ef7182e15","tid":990431,"uid":2442,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"應該冇得攪。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，重乜噉睇唔開用七千幾買hisense，七千幾買SONY都得。"},{"pid":"ab97e1d9ac0f75de702e5abe75583c2fba001a1b","tid":990431,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"無問題<br />\n係開機好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6a39989854a3f5ebce988d9cd9fd19c7f48bf3","tid":990431,"uid":177924,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"901532f2f33f18d8bda0604deed7ef1ef7182e15","tid":990431,"uid":2442,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"應該冇得攪。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，重乜噉睇唔開用七千幾買hisense，七千幾買SONY都得。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"屋企人買果陣我讀緊中學<br />\n屋企人唔識呢啲科技野<br />\n我果陣又唔識諗<br />\n淨係覺得部機好大部<br />\n外型幾靚仔<br />\n又做緊promotion<br />\n又吹到好勁咁<br />\n咁就.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr